d.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20first%20being%20rolled%20out%20to%20members%20of%20Apple's%20beta%20software%20program%20in%20the%20iOS%2017.3%20update.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20introducing%20a%20security%20feature%20designed%20to%20stop%20thieves%20from%20wreaking%20havoc%20by%20accessing%20your%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20and%20other%20publications%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fpersonal-tech%2Fapple-iphone-ios-update-stolen-device-protection-698d760e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20the%20news.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fthe-iphone-setting-thieves-use-to-lock-you-out-of-your-apple-account-716d350d%3Fmod%3Dtrending_now_news_3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Journal%20found%20that%20criminals%20were%20stealing%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20by%20watching%20users%20enter%20their%20passcodes%20before%20stealing%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20they%20had%20the%20device%20and%20passcode%2C%20thieves%20could%20switch%20on%20the%20recovery%20key%20or%20generate%20a%20new%20one%20if%20it%20had%20already%20been%20activated%2C%20the%20Journal%20reported.%20They%20could%20then%20lock%20the%20user%20out%20of%20all%20of%20their%20accounts%20and%20get%20access%20to%20saved%20payment%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActivating%20the%20recovery%20key%2C%20a%20randomly%20generated%2028-character%20code%2C%20turns%20off%20%26quot%3Baccount%20recovery%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20you%20can't%20get%20back%20into%20your%20Apple%20ID%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it's%20designed%20as%20a%20security%20feature%2C%20if%20you%20lose%20access%20to%20the%20code%2C%20you%20could%20be%20permanently%20locked%20out%20of%20everything%20linked%20to%20your%20account%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2F109345%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giant%20advises%20users%20to%20keep%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20key%20with%20a%20family%20member%20or%20to%20keep%20multiple%20copies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReyhan%20Ayas%2C%20an%20iPhone%20owner%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20minutes%20after%20her%20phone%20was%20stolen%20by%20a%20man%20outside%20a%20Manhattan%20bar%2C%20she%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-not-helpful-woman-locked-out-apple-account-lost-10k-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocked%20out%20of%20her%20Apple%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20had%20%2410%2C000%20taken%20from%20her%20bank%20account.%20She%20believed%20he'd%20seen%20her%20enter%20her%20iPhone%20passcode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20new%20feature%2C%20Stolen%20Device%20Protection%2C%20could%20help%20deter%20this%20kind%20of%20financial%20theft.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%20The%20phone's%20location%20is%20central%20to%20how%20the%20feature%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20change%20passwords%20or%20update%20security%20settings%20when%20your%20phone%20is%20not%20in%20a%20recognized%20location%2C%20like%20your%20home%20or%20workplace%2C%20biometric%20information%20will%20be%20required%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fpersonal-tech%2Fapple-iphone-ios-update-stolen-device-protection-698d760e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20additional%20layer%20of%20security%2C%20the%20changes%20will%20only%20be%20confirmed%20once%20you%20enter%20your%20biometric%20information%20a%20second%20time%2C%20after%20an%20hour-long%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20no%20hour%20delay%20if%20you%20are%20making%20changes%20to%20accounts%20from%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20rare%20cases%20where%20a%20thief%20can%20observe%20the%20user%20entering%20the%20passcode%20and%20then%20steal%20the%20device%2C%20Stolen%20Device%20Protection%20adds%20a%20sophisticated%20new%20layer%20of%20protection%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Apple%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fapple-ios-17-3-update-stolen-device-protection%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBS%20MoneyWatch%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20actions%20protected%20by%20the%20new%20system%20includes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EChanging%20your%20Apple%20ID%20password%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EEnabling%20recovery%20key%2C%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EChanging%20trusted%20phone%20number%20or%20contact%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%20and%20removing%20Face%20ID%20or%20Touch%20ID%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EDisabling%20Find%20my%20Phone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ETurning%20off%20Stolen%20Device%20Protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20new%20feature%20is%20not%20widely%20available%20to%20Apple%20users.%20It's%20first%20being%20rolled%20out%20to%20members%20of%20Apple's%20beta%20software%20program%20in%20the%20iOS%2017.3%20update%2C%20which%20began%20rolling%20out%20to%20developers%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20beta%20group%20will%20test%20the%20update%20and%20provide%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20made%20outside%20of%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-new-security-feature-stops-thieves-locking-you-from-accounts-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702474337000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579878750edbc52a863a2e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-new-security-feature-stops-thieves-locking-you-from-accounts-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20will%20introduce%20new%20security%20laye