ister's%20Statement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20parties%20belonging%20to%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today%20after%20the%20security%20breach%2C%20accusing%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20of%20refusing%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20issue.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20afternoon%2C%20two%20men%2C%20carrying%20canisters%20emitting%20unidentified%20yellow%20smoke%2C%20had%20jumped%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20and%20ran%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20overpowered%20by%20MPs%20and%20security%20personnel%20in%20short%20order.%20The%20men%2C%20along%20with%20two%20others%20who%20were%20outside%2C%20have%20been%20arrested.%20Investigators%20have%20said%20six%20peope%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%2C%20coming%20on%20the%2022nd%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20parliament%20attack%2C%20raised%20huge%20questions%2C%20including%20how%20the%20upgraded%20security%20was%20breached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BINDIA%20parties%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20this%20afternoon%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20extraordinary%20events%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20and%20the%20refusal%20of%20the%20Home%20Minister%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20especially%20after%20such%20a%20huge%20breach%20of%20security%20on%20the%20very%20same%20day%20Parliament%20was%20attacked%2022%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20posted%20Congress%20media%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20repeated%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20statement.%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20said%20he%20would%20assess%20the%20situation%20and%20give%20the%20MPs%20and%20update%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20not%20placate%20the%20Opposition%20members%2C%20who%20walked%20out%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20security%20breach%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Parliament%20today%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20later%20posted%20on%20X.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20demand%20that%20the%20Home%20Minister%20come%20to%20both%20Houses%20and%20give%20a%20statement%20on%20this.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20how%20did%20two%20people%20come%20inside%20such%20a%20big%20security%20department%20and%20release%20gas%20from%20a%20cannister%20there%3F%20We%20hope%20that%20the%20government%20will%20take%20this%20very%20seriously%20and%20we%20demand%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20entire%20incident.%20We%20are%20always%20ready%20for%20the%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702471740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fess4evb8_new-parliament-rajya-sabha_625x300_21_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-security-breach-india-bloc-walks-out-of-rajya-sabha-demands-home-ministers-statement-4667090%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Opposition%20parties%20belonging%20to%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today%20after%20the%20security%20breach%2C%20accusing%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20of%20refusing%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20issue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-security-breach-india-bloc-walks-out-of-rajya-sabha-demands-home-ministers-statement-4667090%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-security-breach-india-bloc-walks-out-of-rajya-sabha-demands-home-ministers-statement-4667090%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-security-breach-india-bloc-walks-out-of-rajya-sabha-demands-home-min