%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-says-military-trials-can-resume-for-103-supporters-of-imran-khan%2Famp_articleshow%2F105965766.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-says-military-trials-can-resume-for-103-supporters-of-imran-khan%2Famp_articleshow%2F105965766.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elite%20investor%20Jeremy%20Grantham%20has%20warned%20stocks%20are%20in%20a%20bubble%20and%20could%20plunge%20by%20over%2050%25%20-%20but%20his%20colleague%20says%20they've%20gotten%20cheaper%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221897%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22grantham%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F600ee0bc7e47190011cb9006%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22948%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeremy%20Grantham.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FNicholas%20Roberts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJeremy%20Grantham%20has%20warned%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20could%20plunge%20by%20more%20than%2050%25%20from%20current%20levels%20to%202%2C200%20points.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20one%20of%20his%20colleagues%2C%20Ben%20Inker%2C%20says%20US%20stocks%20are%20much%20cheaper%20today%20than%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGMO's%20co-head%20of%20asset%20allocation%20says%20inflation%20and%20economic%20growth%20have%20made%20stocks%20more%20valuable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Grantham%20expects%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20to%20shed%20a%20third%20of%20its%20value%2C%20and%20plunge%20by%20over%2050%25%20from%20current%20levels%20if%20a%20few%20things%20go%20wrong.%20Ben%20Inker%2C%20the%20co-head%20of%20asset%20allocation%20at%20the%20elite%20investor's%20firm%20GMO%2C%20struck%20a%20much%20more%20positive%20tone%20during%20the%20latest%20episode%20of%20Morningstar's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D3a67bd8cbcccb9e2c57a0d8b8afc655614858617c1371314355278c5b37242c2%26postID%3D65798a94