mpanies%20generally%20grow%20alongside%20the%20wider%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20upshot%20is%20that%20US%20stocks%20are%20%26quot%3Bsubstantially%20better%20than%20they%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Inker%20said.%20He%20went%20as%20far%20as%20saying%20the%20cheapest%2020%25%20of%20stocks%20are%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20cheap%20in%20absolute%20terms%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20statement%20he%20and%20his%20colleagues%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20make%20in%20a%20while%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInker's%20comments%20are%20striking%20given%20that%20Grantham%2C%20GMO's%20cofounder%20and%20long-term%20investment%20strategist%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20sounded%20the%20alarm%20on%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fjeremy-grantham-gmo-superbubble-stock-market-bubble-crash-federal-reserve-2022-1%5C%22%3Esuperbubble%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20spanning%20multiple%20asset%20classes%2C%20and%20called%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20to%20nosedive%20from%20about%204%2C600%20points%20today%20to%203%2C200%20points%20or%20even%202%2C200%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrantham%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fgrantham-spx-stock-market-outlook-crash-house-prices-recession-bitcoin-2023-10%5C%22%3Epreviously%20pegged%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20market%20bottom%20at%203%2C000%20points%2C%20or%202%2C000%20points%20if%20%26quot%3Ba%20couple%20of%20wheels%20fall%20off.%26quot%3B%20But%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeremy-grantham-warns-us-stock-market-crash-downside-outlook-2023-12%5C%22%3Erecently%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20Business%20Insider's%20William%20Edwards%20that%20inflation%20and%20economic%20growth%20had%20prompted%20him%20to%20raise%20those%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrantham-inker-stock-market-bubble-crash-outlook-spx-inflation-rece