to%20be%20reached%20by%202050%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20it%20calls%20on%20all%20countries%20to%20move%20away%20from%20using%20fossil%20fuels.%20It%20also%20includes%20important%20milestones%2C%20such%20as%20tripling%20renewable%20energy%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20stops%20short%20of%20setting%20a%20clear%20timeline%20to%20phase%20out%20fossil%20fuels%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20countries%20such%20as%20China%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20had%20strongly%20resisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20at%20%23COP28%20to%20finally%20recognize%20that%20the%20climate%20crisis%20is%2C%20at%20its%20heart%2C%20a%20fossil%20fuel%20crisis%20is%20an%20important%20milestone%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20vice%20president%20Al%20Gore%2C%20who%20chairs%20a%20climate%20advocacy%20non-profit%2C%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falgore%2Fstatus%2F1734853205014557029%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20post%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it%20is%20also%20the%20bare%20minimum%20we%20need%20and%20is%20long%20overdue.%20The%20influence%20of%20petrostates%20is%20still%20evident%20in%20the%20half%20measures%20and%20loopholes%20included%20in%20the%20final%20agreement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClimate%20experts%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20agreed%20that%20the%20deal%20falls%20short%20of%20what%20is%20needed%2C%20as%20emissions%20must%20be%20cut%20by%20almost%20half%20by%202030%20to%20prevent%20global%20warming%20from%20going%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius%20higher%20than%20pre-industrial%20levels%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20better%20than%20it%20could%20have%20been%2C%20but%20could%20try%20harder%2C%26quot%3B%20Tim%20Benton%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Environment%20and%20Society%20Centre%20at%20Chatham%20House%2C%20a%20London-based%20think-tank%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarina%20B.%20Romanello%2C%20a%20health%20researcher%20at%20University%20College%20London%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Lancet%20Countdown%2C%20an%20international%20research%20collaboration%20that%20tracks%20climate%20change%2C%20agreed.%20She%20noted%20this%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiplomatic%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20way%20past%20the%20point%20in%20which%20small%20progress%20can%20be%20celebrated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20text%20opens%20loopholes%20that%20could%20mean%20a%20perpetuation%20of%20our%20addiction%20to%20fossil%20fuels.%20This%20is%20incompatible%20with%20a%20healthy%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJohn%20Kerry%2C%20the%20special%20climate%20envoy%20for%20the%20US%2C%20said%20the%20agreement%20was%20a%20cause%20for%20%26quot%3Boptimism.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BMany%20people%20would%20have%20liked%20clear%20language%20about%20the%20need%20to%20begin%20peaking%20and%20reducing%20fossil%20fuels%20in%20this%20critical%20decade.%20But%20we%20know%20this%20was%20a%20compromise%20between%20many%20parties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wording%20of%20the%20legal%20text%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20fiery%20debates%20in%20the%20two%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20earlier%20version%20of%20the%20text%20proposed%20to%20call%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bphase%20out%26quot%3B%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20by%202050%2C%20but%20this%20wording%20was%20rejected%20from%20a%20draft%20published%20Monday%20by%20the%20COP%20presidency%2C%20which%20proposed%20to%20call%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bphase%20down%26quot%3B%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20pedantic%20play%20of%20words%2C%20the%20distinction%20between%20%26quot%3Bphase%20out%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bphase%20down%26quot%3B%20matters%20as%20the%20latter%20doesn't%20call%20for%20countries%20to%20stop%20using%20fossil%20fuels%20by%202050%2C%20Romanello%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20drew%20ire%20from%20some%20member%20states%20that%20threatened%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fenvironment%2F2023%2Fdec%2F12%2Fcop-28-australia-us-and-uk-say-they-wont-sign-agreement-that-would-be-death-certificate-for-small-islands%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalk%20out%20of%20negotiations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20have%20brought%20them%20to%20a%20standstill.%20The%20text%20needed%20to%20be%20approved%20unanimously%20by%20nearly%20200%20member%20states%20to%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20the%20deal%20agreed%20upon%20a%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20and%20accelerating%20efforts%20toward%20net%20zero%20emission%20using%20zero%20and%20low%20carbon%20fuels%20well%20before%20or%20by%20around%20mid-century.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenton%20noted%20%26quot%3Bthe%20devil%20is%20in%20the%20details.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20quite%20a%20lot%20of%20scope%20in%20the%20verbiage%20for%20multiple%20readings%20of%20the%20text%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20language%20still%20allows%20countries%20to%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-first-commercial-carbon-capture-facility-opens-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbon%20capture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20storage%20in%20their%20energy%20transition%20strategy%2C%20an%20approach%20that%20has%20been%20criticized%20by%20climate%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%20that%20technology%20does%20not%20exist%2C%20has%20not%20been%20developed%20at%20stage.%20So%20it's%20something%20we%20cannot%20count%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marinello.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20UN%20summit%20failed%20on%20another%20front%3A%20attracting%20funding%20to%20help%20countries%20bankroll%20their%20transition%20to%20clean%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funding%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20global%20Net%20Zero%20strategy%2C%20in%20part%20because%20it%20can%20support%20lower-income%20countries%20to%20step%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%20while%20continuing%20to%20develop%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20presidency%20we're%20trying%20to%20suggest%20that%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fsustainability%2Fbusiness-key-cop28-success-needs-bring-checkbook-special-representative-2023-11-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecome%20with%20their%20checkbooks.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20But%20I%20didn't%20see%20that%20not%20on%20any%20reasonable%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bracking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20fund%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fagenda%2F2023%2F12%2Fcop28-loss-and-damage-fund-climate-change%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eformally%20established%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20COP28%20to%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20to%20countries%20impacted%20by%20the%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20gathered%20initial%20commitments%20that%20reached%20about%20%24750%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBracking%20qualified%20that%20amount%20as%20%26quot%3Bpaltry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20really%20small%20and%20it's%20an%20insult%2C%20really%2C%20that%20you%20set%20up%20a%20whole%20new%20fund%20and%20then%20you%20only%20commit%20750%20million%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20university%2C%20Kings%2C%20we%20have%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20about%20%24800%20million%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20one%20university.%20Now%20you%20think%20about%20how%20much%20it%20would%20actually%20cost%20to%20help%20eight%20billion%20people%2C%20800%20million%20of%20them%20whose%20livelihoods%20are%20already%20at%20risk%20or%20threatened%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcop28-climate-experts-unimpressed-by-worlds-attempt-to-prevent-catastrophe-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702470890000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65799eb17a3c8094d5dc6b8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcop28-climate-experts-unimpressed-by-worlds-attempt-to-prevent-catastrophe-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20deal%20was%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20COP28%20president%2C%20climate%20experts%20noted%20loopholes%20in%20the%20text%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20funding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mguenot%40businessinsider.com%20(Marianne%20Guenot)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcop28-climate-experts-unimpressed-by-worlds-attempt-to-prevent-catastrophe-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pranab%20Mukherjee%E2%80%99s%20Daughter%E2%80%99s%20Account%20of%20His%20Diary%20'Eats%20and%20Breathes%20Politics'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F31203418%2Fpranab-mukherjee.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAnybody%20who%20interacted%20with%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20during%20one%20of%20his%20informal%20interactions%2C%20either%20as%20the%20First%20Citizen%20or%20in%20his%20numerous%20avatars%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%2C%20is%20familiar%20with%20his%20response%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20written%20in%20my%20diary%20but%20the%20content%20will%20not%20be%20known%20during%20my%20lifetime%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20so%20in%20one%20form%2Flanguage%20or%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20384px)%2085vw%2C%20384px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13170549%2F81afLFXd0mL._SL1500_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22384%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13170549%2F81afLFXd0mL._SL1500_.jpg%20784w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13170549%2F81afLFXd0mL._SL1500_-196x300.jpg%20196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13170549%2F81afLFXd0mL._SL1500_-669x1024.jpg%20669w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689064%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESharmistha%20Mukherjee%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EPranab%2C%20My%20Father%3A%20A%20Daughter%20Remembers%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ERupa%20Publications%20(December%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20%3Cem%3EPranab%2C%20My%20Father%3A%20A%20Daughter%20Remembers%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20such%20an%20important%20book.%20It%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20observations%20and%20apprehensions%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20respected%20and%20astute%20politician%20while%20infusing%20what%20is%20essentially%20a%20crucial%20piece%20of%20Indian%20history%20with%20honesty%2C%20spontaneity%2C%20and%20welcome%20wit%20that%20are%20hallmarks%20of%20the%20daughter%20%E2%80%93%20Sharmistha%20Mukherjee.%C2%A0From%20spurning%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20cryptic%20offer%20for%20the%20Jangipur%20seat%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ELodbi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(will%20you%20fight)%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20to%20becoming%20a%20Congress%20politician%20after%20her%20father%20asked%20her%20if%20she%20wanted%20to%20become%20one%20and%20then%20starting%20veritably%20from%20the%20bottom%20to%20quit%20it%20all%20and%20now%20to%20write%20this%20book%20that%20has%20created%20a%20mini%20political%20storm%20in%20a%20teacup%20over%20Mukherjee%E2%80%99s%20observations%20about%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Sharmistha%20has%20travelled%20some%20distance%2C%20her%20brief%20political%20sojourn%20notwithstanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20had%20kings%20holding%20umbrellas%20for%20her%20(then%20Bhutan%20king%20Jigme%20Singye%20Wangchuk)%2C%20and%20the%20man%20who%20her%20father%20thought%20was%20the%20only%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20county%20after%20Indira%20Gandhi%20with%20his%20hand%20on%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20pulse%20%E2%80%93%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20honouring%20her%20impromptu%20dance%20programme%20invites%20and%20giving%20her%20appointments%20to%20talk%20about%20life%20and%20politics%20in%20general.%20The%20stories%20flow%20thick%20and%20fast%20along%20with%20extracts%20from%20the%20valuable%20diaries%20(tomes%20that%20even%20she%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20read%20during%20his%20lifetime%2C%20as%20she%20mentioned%20during%20the%20launch%20event%20earlier%20this%20week).%20What%20one%20misses%20in%20those%20pages%20are%20indications%20about%20her%20own%20equation%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20she%20briefly%20served%20and%20is%20often%20left%20wondering%20whether%20those%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO)%20meetings%20have%20outlived%20the%20greatest%20prime%20minister%20India%20never%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20in%20a%20sense%20eats%20and%20breathes%20politics%20but%20is%20a%20must-read%20not%20just%20for%20students%20of%20politics%20or%20history.%20It%20is%20a%20breezy%20and%20enjoyable%20read%2C%20an%20honest%20account%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20first%20part%20(before%20politics%20eclipsed%20the%20personal%20in%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20life)%20as%20much%20of%20the%20young%20man%20who%20quickly%20became%20among%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20most%20trusted%20lieutenants%20as%20of%20Geeta%20(Pranab%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Subhra)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20woman%20who%20stood%20surety%20for%20one%20prime%20minister%20(P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao)%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwept%20uncontrollably%E2%80%9D%20for%20another%20(Indira%20Gandhi)%20and%20at%20whose%20funeral%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20another%20country%20(Sheikh%20Hasina)%20could%20not%20hold%20back%20her%20tears.%20Even%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20pets%20feature%20prominently%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20one%20who%20bit%20a%20future%20prime%20minister%20to%20the%20one%20that%20bit%20the%20master%20during%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20points%20of%20his%20life%20%E2%80%93%20when%20he%20was%20left%20out%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20cabinet%20in%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20rarely%20is%20there%20a%20book%20that%20has%20politics%20at%20its%20core%20this%20wholesome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmistha%E2%80%99s%20disclaimer%20in%20the%20foreword%20that%20she%20is%20not%20a%20writer%20comes%20across%20as%20rhetorical%20humility.%20She%20does%20a%20deft%20job%20of%20chronicling%20what%20it%20was%20like%20being%20the%20daughter%20of%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20(as%20advised%20by%20her%20friend%2C%20author%20Amitav%20Ghosh)%20while%20also%20etching%20a%20warm%2C%20loving%20picture%20of%20the%20human%20being%20behind%20the%20political%20persona%20of%20a%20workaholic%2C%20a%20leader%20whose%20political%20acumen%20was%20respected%20across%20the%20political%20divide%20(Bhutan%20king%20told%20his%20three%20wives%20that%20he%20was%20holding%20the%20umbrella%20for%20Sharmistha%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20her%20father%E2%80%9D)%20and%20across%20borders%20and%20yet%2C%20who%20managed%20to%20win%20a%20mere%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20his%20political%20life%20of%2048%20years%20(he%20first%20entered%20parliament%20as%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20in%201969).%20Through%20all%20of%20this%2C%20the%20backdrop%20of%20contemporary%20politics%20is%20never%20allowed%20to%20fade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20touches%20upon%20his%20own%20internal%20turmoils%20%E2%80%93%20how%20he%20struggled%20to%20keep%20his%20temper%20and%20chastised%20himself%20in%20the%20pages%20of%20his%20diary%20for%20failing%20to%20do%20so%20and%20his%20propensity%20to%20use%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cfirmly%20and%20frankly%E2%80%9D%20to%20describe%20his%20own%20interventions%20while%20documenting%20many%20of%20his%20political%20meetings.%20She%20also%20shared%20witty%20yet%20politically%20loaded%20anecdotes%20of%20how%20the%20political%20blended%20into%20the%20personal%20(Pranab%20parrying%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20query%20about%20why%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20share%20his%20prime%20ministerial%20ambitions%20with%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20with%20a%20hilarious%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20like%20you%20that%20I%20would%20throw%20a%20tantrum%20when%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20what%20I%20want%E2%80%9D).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20a%20no-nonsense%20but%20loving%20father%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20mould%20of%20many%20middle-class%20fathers%20of%20his%20generation.%20For%20example%20when%20ex-UK%20PM%20Margaret%20Thatcher%20met%20her%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20India%20and%20asked%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20the%20beauty%20and%20grace%20of%20a%20dancer.%20Are%20you%20a%20dancer%3F%E2%80%9D%20sending%20a%20young%20Sharmistha%20over%20the%20moon%2C%20Pranab%20gives%20his%20daughter%20a%20reality%20check%20that%20visiting%20dignitaries%20are%20briefed%20about%20family%20members%20of%20key%20people%20in%20the%20host%20country.%20But%20when%20Sharmistha%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20he%20objected%20to%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20she%20is%20not%20in%20the%20league%20of%20performers%20that%20normally%20get%20to%20be%20on%20that%20exalted%20stage%20goes%20off%20flawlessly%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20newly%20sworn-in%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20Sharmistha%20had%20invited%20almost%20on%20an%20impulse%20much%20to%20the%20discomfiture%20of%20her%20father%2C%20the%20proud%20father%20records%20it%20in%20his%20precious%20diary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20has%20been%20made%20of%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20observations%20about%20a%20younger%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20his%20diaries%2C%20coloured%20no%20doubt%20also%20by%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20release%20%E2%80%93%20less%20than%20six%20months%20to%20the%20next%20parliamentary%20elections.%20Sharmistha%20launched%20a%20spirited%20counterattack%20to%20the%20Congress%20ecosystem%20at%20the%20launch%20event%20when%20she%20asked%20whether%20the%20proponents%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20want%20to%20control%20what%20a%20man%20writes%20in%20his%20diary%20and%20what%20his%20daughter%20reminisces%20about%20him.%C2%A0%20Those%20diaries%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20book%20%E2%80%93%20also%20have%20countless%20instances%20of%20the%20trust%20deficit%20between%20Pranab%20and%20the%20Gandhis%20post-Indira%2C%20sometimes%20trying%20to%20address%20their%20genesis%20and%20at%20others%20offering%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20own%20assessment%20like%20when%20he%20says%20of%20Sonia%3A%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20only%20trying%20to%20protect%20her%20own%20and%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20interests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20at%20the%20India%20International%20Centre%20on%20Monday%20was%20significantly%20bereft%20of%20any%20Congress%20leaders%20except%20former%20Union%20minister%20P.%20Chidambaram%2C%20whose%20coming%20was%20a%20surprise%20even%20for%20the%20author%20and%20who%2C%20ironically%20is%20also%20the%20man%20often%20accused%20by%20political%20opponents%20of%20having%20bugged%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20office%20when%20both%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20cabinet.%20But%20there%20are%20unsavoury%20comments%20%E2%80%93%20admittedly%20far%20less%20scathing%20%E2%80%93%20made%20against%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20divide%20in%20the%20book%20while%20tackling%20some%20of%20the%20criticism%20that%20had%20dogged%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20public%20life%20(retrospective%20tax%2C%20constitutional%20crises%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20former%20president%E2%80%99s%20appearance%20on%20a%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20stage%20during%20the%20launch%20conversation%20with%20former%20diplomat%20Pawan%20Verma%2C%20the%20author%20could%20barely%20hide%20her%20glee%20about%20a%20tweet%20that%20she%20had%20come%20across%20during%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20which%20he%20had%20espoused%20the%20Congress%20ideology%20from%20a%20stage%20that%20is%20usually%20witness%20to%20professions%20of%20a%20different%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CPranab%20Mukherjee%20is%20trolling%20the%20RSS%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharmistha%20said%20while%20breaking%20into%20laughter.%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20own%20justification%20about%20the%20criticism%20that%20his%20appearance%20gave%20%E2%80%9Clegitimacy%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20RSS%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20am%20I%20to%20give%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20RSS!%20The%20people%20of%20India%20have%20given%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20RSS%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20there%20is%20one%20thought%20one%20comes%20out%20with%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20clear%20intent%20that%20Pranab%20seems%20to%20have%20conveyed%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20hopes%20his%20dear%20%E2%80%9CMunni%E2%80%9D%20will%20one%20day%20write%20a%20book%20from%20the%20contents%20of%20his%20diary.%20Is%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20trolling%20the%20Gandhis%20from%20beyond%20the%20grave%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAbantika%20Ghosh%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20public%20policy%20professional.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702470704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F31203418%2Fpranab-mukherjee.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fpranab-mukherjee-the-best-prime-minister-india-never-had%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharmistha%20Mukherjee's%20book%20'Pranab%2C%20My%20Father%3A%20A%20Daughter%20Remembers'%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20observations%20and%20apprehensions%20recorded%20in%20the%20former%20president's%20personal%20diary%2C%20which%20were%20never%20made%20public%20during%20his%20lifetime.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fpranab-mukherjee-the-best-prime-minister-india-never-had%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20most%20searched%20movies%20of%202023%E2%80%8B