ow-dead-hong-kong-star-1235836074%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Furl-kathy-chow-dead-hong-kong-star-1235836074%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Furl-kathy-chow-dead-hong-kong-star-1235836074%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20been%20to%20more%20than%2050%20countries%20on%20a%20budget.%20Here%20are%20my%20top%203%20money-saving%20tips.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meagan%20Drillinger%20a%20digital%20nomad%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65774d3b7a3c8094d5dbb006%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeagan%20Drillinger%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20maximize%20their%20budget%20while%20being%20full-time%20travelers.%3Cp%3EMeagan%20Drillinger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeagan%20Drillinger%20is%20a%20travel%20writer%20who%20uses%20research%20and%20discipline%20to%20save%20money%20when%20traveling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECheck%20when%20peak%20season%20is%20before%20you%20commit%20and%20be%20open%20to%20house-sitting%20exchanges%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20traveling%2C%20she%20likes%20to%20have%20access%20to%20a%20kitchen%20and%20tries%20to%20make%20at%20least%20two%20meals%20a%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20lifetime%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20I%20swapped%20a%20MetroCard%20for%20a%20plane%20ticket%20in%202021%20and%20have%20been%20traveling%20ever%20since.%20I've%20been%20to%2012%20countries%20since%20then%2C%20and%2050%20countries%20over%20the%20past%2015%20years%20as%20a%20full-time%20travel%20writer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20career%20as%20a%20travel%20writer%20does%20afford%20me%20some%20perks%20like%20a%20free%20hotel%20stay%20here%20or%20a%20free%20airline%20ticket%20there%2C%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20I've%20actually%20accepted%20fewer%20comps%20and%20still%20managed%20to%20grow%20my%20savings%20more%20than%20ever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20use%20any%20sneaky%20schemes%20%E2%80%94%20all%20it%20took%20was%20research%20and%20a%20little%20discipline.%20Here%20are%20the%20top%203%20money-saving%20tips%20that%20help%20me%20afford%20my%20nomadic%20lifestyle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20pick%20destinations%20where%20the%20US%20dollar%20goes%20further.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20often%20you'll%20find%20me%20in%20Scandinavia%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20or%20even%20pricey%20domestic%20destinations%20like%20Hawaii%20or%20Miami.%20It's%20just%20too%20difficult%20to%20stick%20to%20an%20accommodation%20budget%20in%20these%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20this%20isn't%20always%20an%20exact%20science.%20Just%20because%20a%20country%20has%20a%20favorable%20exchange%20rate%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20it's%20always%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20once%20got%20stuck%20in%20the%20Philippines%20because%20it%20was%20the%20Lunar%20New%20Year%20%E2%80%94%20a%20detail%20I%20didn't%20think%20about%20until%20I%20got%20there.%20During%20this%20mega%20holiday%2C%20prices%20are%20at%20their%20highest%20and%20inter-island%20flights%20are%20practically%20sold%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20left%20me%20stranded%20on%20Boracay%20for%2011%20days%20until%20I%20could%20afford%20a%20flight%20out.%20Granted%2C%20there%20are%20worse%20places%20in%20the%20world%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bstuck%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20do%20much%20except%20sit%20on%20the%20beach.%20The%20lesson%3F%20Always%20check%20for%20peak%20season%20before%20you%20commit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20most%20part%2C%20sticking%20to%20countries%20with%20good%20USD%20exchange%20rates%20is%20a%20solid%20move.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20spent%20November%202023%20in%20Cape%20Town%2C%20South%20Africa.%20The%20exchange%20rate%20there%20was%20USD%201%20%3D%2018.96%20ZAR%2C%20which%20is%20extremely%20good%20for%20US%20bank%20accounts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20breakdown%20of%20some%20of%20our%20expenses%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20rented%20a%20one-bedroom%20Airbnb%20for%201200%20USD.%20Splitting%20it%20with%20my%20husband%2C%20I%20spent%20%24600%20%E2%80%94%20thus%20sticking%20to%20my%20%241%2C000%20max%20accommodation%20budget.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20took%20Ubers%20everywhere%20in%20Cape%20Town.%20Sounds%20extravagant%2C%20I%20know%2C%20but%20when%20the%20average%20city%20ride%20is%2050%20ZAR%20(%242.60%2C%20or%20less%20than%20a%20New%20York%20City%20subway%20swipe)%2C%20it's%20remarkably%20affordable%20to%20be%20so%20lavish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EActivities%20were%20also%20affordable%3A%20A%20dinner%20out%20for%20two%20with%20a%20bottle%20of%20wine%20is%20about%2040%20USD%20in%20total.%20Plus%2C%20Cape%20Town%20is%20webbed%20with%20hiking%20trails%20and%20fringed%20with%20beaches%20so%20it's%20easy%20to%20stay%20entertained%20for%20no%20money%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20I'm%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20house-sitting.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20used%20hotel%20deal%20apps%20like%20Hotels.com%20and%20HotelTonight%2C%20and%20even%20booked%20private%20rooms%20in%20hostels%20when%20I'm%20really%20in%20a%20pinch%2C%20but%20my%20favorite%20way%20to%20save%20on%20accommodations%20is%20to%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrusted-housesitters-free-pet-sitting-for-strangers-what-its-like-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETrusted%20Housesitters%20network%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrusted%20Housesitters%20is%20an%20online%20network%20of%20approved%20pet%2Fhomeowners%20and%20traveling%20pet%20sitters%20who%20set%20up%20exchanges%3A%20free%20pet-sitting%20for%20a%20free%20place%20to%20stay.%20Discovering%20it%20was%20life-changing%20for%20us.%20The%20platform%20has%20opportunities%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20so%20whenever%20I'm%20headed%20to%20a%20pricier%20destination%20I%20always%20check%20to%20see%20the%20pet-sitting%20potential.%20It's%20saved%20me%20money%20across%20California%2C%20Colorado%2C%20and%20even%20Hawaii.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20sounds%20a%20little%20weird%20to%20you%2C%20you're%20not%20alone%3A%20Everyone%20we%20tell%20about%20it%20thinks%20we're%20slightly%20nuts%20for%20staying%20in%20someone%20else's%20home%20and%20watching%20their%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETruthfully%2C%20I%20was%20skeptical%20about%20the%20concept%20myself%2C%20but%20in%20the%20nearly%20three%20years%20we've%20been%20using%20the%20program%2C%20I've%20never%20had%20a%20negative%20experience.%20I%20%3Cem%3Ehave%3C%2Fem%3E%20heard%20a%20few%20horror%20stories%20from%20others%20%E2%80%94%20dirty%20houses%2C%20sitters%20who%20chain-smoke%20inside%20%E2%80%94%20but%20our%20experiences%20have%20always%20been%20positive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20because%20we%20are%20overly%20thorough%20in%20our%20vetting%20process.%20We've%20learned%20to%20only%20apply%20to%20house%20sits%20that%20have%20tons%20of%20pictures%20and%20reviews%20from%20past%20sitters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20set%20up%20a%20FaceTime%20with%20homeowners%20well%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20sometimes%20arrive%20a%20day%20early%20to%20have%20dinner%20and%20meet%20our%20hosts%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20piece%20of%20advice%20is%20to%20keep%20an%20open%20mind%20and%20manage%20expectations%3B%20this%20is%20not%20Airbnb%20or%20a%20hotel.%20While%20you%20can%20search%20for%20and%20apply%20to%20housesits%20by%20location%2C%20very%20rarely%20will%20that%20location%20be%20in%20the%20hottest%20part%20of%20town.%20You've%20got%20to%20be%20flexible%20and%20willing%20to%20compromise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20planning%20to%20use%20Trusted%20Housesitters%20outside%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20check%20the%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D1342f24cb52386195c2ea8afdb5124b52990f69a4def5defb3cbe4dae754da5e%26postID%3D65738a564c878294df210e8a%26postSlug%3Dhow-to-maximize-saving-money-while-traveling-the-world-2023-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.trustedhousesitters.com%252Fpages%252Finternational-house-sitting-and-immigration%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elegal%20entry%20requirements%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20rules%20and%20restrictions%2C%20including%20necessary%20visas%2C%20etc.%20vary%20from%20place%20to%20place%20and%20should%20all%20be%20confirmed%20before%20you%20accept%20a%20house%20sit%20in%20a%20foreign%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20I'm%20strategic%20about%20what%2C%20when%2C%20and%20where%20I%20eat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20anything%20like%20me%2C%20food%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20travel.%20I%20adore%20trying%20restaurants%20in%20new%20destinations%20and%20sampling%20the%20local%20cuisine%2C%20so%20it%20can%20also%20be%20where%20I%20rack%20up%20the%20highest%20bills%20if%20I'm%20not%20careful.%20That's%20why%20I%20have%20to%20make%20a%20few%20compromises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20traveling%2C%20I%20try%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20have%20access%20to%20a%20kitchen%20of%20some%20type%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20house%20sit%20or%20an%20Airbnb.%20I%20stock%20up%20on%20groceries%20to%20ensure%20I%20can%20make%20at%20least%20two%20meals%20a%20day%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20I'll%20make%20my%20breakfast%20and%20lunch%20and%20then%20dine%20out%20for%20dinner.%20(A%20great%20Happy%20Hour%20special%20will%20usually%20get%20my%20vote).%20If%20I'm%20in%20a%20destination%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I'll%20often%20have%20days%20when%20I%20make%20all%20three%20meals%20at%20home.%20And%20if%20I'm%20on%20a%20road%20trip%2C%20I%20have%20a%20cooler%20packed%20with%20sandwiches%20and%20snacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20would%20be%20wonderful%20to%20go%20all%20out%20on%20every%20single%20trip.%20But%20for%20someone%20who%20spends%20nearly%20100%25%20of%20their%20time%20traveling%2C%20that's%20simply%20not%20a%20sustainable%20or%20feasible%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20travels%20as%20often%20as%20I%20do%2C%20but%20everyone%20loves%20a%20money-saving%20tip.%20These%20have%20served%20me%20well%20as%20I've%20transitioned%20to%20a%20full-time%20life%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Meagan%20Drillinger%20is%20a%20travel%20writer%20and%20digital%20nomad%20originally%20from%20New%20York.%20She%20now%20lives%20on%20the%20road%20full-time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-maximize-saving-money-while-traveling-the-world-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702470034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65774d3b7a3c8094d5dbb006%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-maximize-saving-money-while-traveling-the-world-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Follow%20these%20tips%20to%20save%20the%20most%20money%20while%20traveling%20the%20globe.%20Digital%20nomad%20Meagan%20Drillinger%20swears%20by%203%20money-saving%20tips%20after%20visiting%20over%2050%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Meagan%20Drillinger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-maximize-saving-money-while-traveling-the-world-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20'Survivors'%20Of%20Rinku's%20Viral%206%20That%20Broke%20Glass%20Panel%20Are%20Shaken%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThough%20India%20lost%20the%20second%20T20I%20against%20South%20Africa%20by%20five%20wickets%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20the%20hosts%20taking%20an%20unassailable%201-0%20lead%20in%20the%20thr