ssociated%20Press%20in%20Paris.%20There%2C%20I%20reported%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmaximum-human-age-scientists-think-up-for-debate-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeanne%20Calment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20lived%20to%20122%20years%20and%20164%20days%20%E2%80%94%20the%20longest%20documented%20life%20span%20in%20history.%20Just%20before%20her%20121st%20birthday%2C%20Calment%20released%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsCQpCje6Wa0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20a%20rap%20album%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20title%20translated%20to%20%26quot%3BTime's%20Mistress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mother%20is%2093%20and%20still%20living%20alone%20in%20the%20house%20I%20grew%20up%20in%2C%20but%20my%20dad%20died%20at%2067%2C%20and%20my%20brother%20died%20at%2059.%20I'm%2063%2C%20which%20means%20I%20could%20be%20just%20past%20middle%20age%20by%20family%20standards%20or%20have%20one%20foot%20in%20the%20grave.%20That's%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20I%20set%20out%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-62178-20%26h%3Da9f3b4e9c3e65c410270d2569480737b701cdbb65bb95419fadfcb178389ba33%26postID%3D657756c533f7fba9f64c0142%26postSlug%3Dlongevity-things-to-consider-become-centenarian-2023-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FBig-100-New-World-Super-Aging%252Fdp%252F163576856X%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20learn%20everything%20I%20could%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20people%20who%20live%20to%20be%20100%20or%20older%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20our%20society%20will%20change%20as%20more%20and%20more%20people%20reach%20triple%20digits.%20Here's%20what%20I%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20positive%20mindset%20goes%20a%20long%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20often%20think%20of%20exercise%20and%20a%20healthy%20diet%20as%20the%20only%20proven%20ways%20to%20boost%20longevity%2C%20so%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20mindset%20plays%20a%20massive%20role.%20A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F12150226%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20study%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Yale%20found%20that%20people%20with%20a%20positive%20mindset%20about%20the%20aging%20process%20lived%20about%207%20%C2%BD%20years%20longer%20than%20people%20with%20less%20positive%20perceptions%20of%20aging.%20We%20tend%20to%20think%20of%20the%20body%20and%20mind%20as%20separate%2C%20but%20they're%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFaith%20will%20help%20you%20live%20longer%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20piece%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1177%2F1948550618779820%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20research%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20surprised%20me%20was%20that%20people%20who%20practice%20a%20religious%20faith%20live%20about%20four%20years%20longer%20than%20people%20who%20don't.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20which%20religion%20you%20observe%3A%20Researchers%20believe%20the%20social%20aspect%20of%20attending%20religious%20services%20helps%20increase%20life%20span.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20found%20that%20nonreligious%20people%20who%20volunteer%20and%20who%20have%20rich%20social%20networks%20live%20almost%20as%20long%20as%20people%20who%20consider%20themselves%20religious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMarriage%20might%20be%20a%20pain%2C%20but%20it%20will%20increase%20your%20life%20span%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20comic%20knows%20the%20frustrations%20of%20marriage%20are%20good%20for%20a%20few%20laughs.%20While%20any%20long-term%20relationship%20has%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20having%20a%20partner%20might%20help%20you%20live%20longer.%20One%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7452000%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20study%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20among%20men%20between%2065%20and%2085%20years%20old%2C%20those%20who%20were%20married%20lived%20two%20years%20longer%20on%20average%20than%20unmarried%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStress%20is%20an%20absolute%20killer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effect%20of%20chronic%20stress%20on%20your%20life%20span%20surprised%20me%20as%20well.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-62178-20%26h%3D56faa10b44f6d870e9df5caee1dba766bc798fb4fd9bb361cc263a9390cf94d6%26postID%3D657756c533f7fba9f64c0142%26postSlug%3Dlongevity-things-to-consider-become-centenarian-2023-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41398-021-01735-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EResearch%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20toxic%20stress%20can%20impact%20every%20cell%20in%20your%20body%20and%20accelerate%20the%20aging%20process.%20After%20learning%20that%2C%20I%20was%20inspired%20to%20leave%20my%20job%20in%20the%2024%2F7%20news%20cycle%20and%20pursue%20writing%20books%20%E2%80%94%20a%20much%20more%20relaxed%20pace%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELongevity%20isn't%20equitable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20chronic%20stress%20might%20help%20explain%20one%20of%20the%20more%20concerning%20findings%3A%20the%20racial%20disparities%20in%20longevity.%20Black%20Americans%2C%20on%20average%2C%20die%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kff.org%2Fracial-equity-and-health-policy%2Freport%2Fkey-data-on-health-and-health-care-by-race-and-ethnicity%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DProvisional%2520data%2520from%25202021%2520show%2C77.7%2520years%2520for%2520Hispanic%2520people.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esix%20years%20earlier%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20their%20white%20counterparts.%20That's%20a%20lot%20of%20life%20they're%20missing%20out%20on.%20There's%20so%20much%20we%20must%20do%20to%20address%20this%2C%20including%20lifting%20people%20out%20of%20poverty.%20After%20all%2C%20being%20in%20a%20higher%20socioeconomic%20bracket%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjama%2Ffullarticle%2F2794146%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCompared%2520with%25202019%2C%2520life%2520expectancy%2Cin%2520the%2520highest%2520income%2520percentile.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eassociated%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20longer%20lifespan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOur%20society%20is%20going%20to%20shift%20as%20we%20get%20older%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20people%20living%20to%20100%20and%20older%20is%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2016%2F04%2F21%2Fworlds-centenarian-population-projected-to-grow-eightfold-by-2050%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20projected%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20grow%20eightfold%20by%202050.%20Half%20of%20today's%205-year-olds%20will%20live%20to%20be%20100.%20That%20brings%20up%20a%20number%20of%20questions%20about%20education%2C%20ageism%2C%20and%20economics%3A%20How%20will%20we%20earn%20enough%20to%20pay%20a%20century's%20worth%20of%20bills%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20concern%20is%20how%20the%20climate%20crisis%20will%20affect%20our%20lives%20as%20we%20get%20older.%20No%20one%20wants%20to%20live%20to%20over%20100%20years%20old%20on%20a%20planet%20that's%20more%20and%20more%20unstable.%20That's%20the%20scary%20part%20of%20my%20research%2C%20but%20it's%20important.%20On%20the%20bright%20side%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20bonus%20years%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20to%20create%20and%20to%20love.%20That%20could%20be%20a%20beautiful%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-things-to-consider-become-centenarian-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702468324000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657757f658e7c0c29a2bbd18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-things-to-consider-become-centenarian-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20whose%20grandmother%20lived%20to%20104%20studies%20longevity.%20He%20said%20having%20a%20positive%20mindset%20and%20getting%20married%20might%20help%20you%20become%20a%20centenarian.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-things-to-consider-become-centenarian-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bobby%20Deol%20drops%20a%20thirst%20trap%3A%20WATCH%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702468219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105964256%2Cimgsize-31636.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbobby-deol-drops-a-thirst-trap-as-he-takes-a-shower-in-this-bts-video-while-shooting-for-animal-watch%2Farticleshow%2F105964274.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105964274.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBobby%20Deol%20shares%20a%20BTS%20video%20from%20the%20sets%20of%20'Animal'%20while%20expressing%20that%20he%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20shooting%20the%20film%20and%20he%20wishes%20it%20was%20longer...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parliament%20Security%20Breach%20Amid%20Khalistani%20Terrorist's%20Attack%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20security%20breach%20at%20parliament%20took%20place%20on%20a%20day%20that%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20had%20threatened%20an%20attack.%20Investigations%20are%20yet%20to%20reveal%20a%20link%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPannun%20--%20the%20US-based%20chief%20of%20extremist%20organisation%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice--%20had%20threatened%20to%20attack%20the%20Indian%20Parliament%20%26quot%3Bon%20or%20before%20December%2013%26quot%3B%20--%20t