ic%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20%E2%80%9Caccommodate%E2%80%9D%20him%20in%20his%20cabinet%2C%20given%20his%20experience%2C%20pedigree%2C%20and%20loyalty%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%E2%80%99s%20worldview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%20high%20command%20did%20just%20the%20opposite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20after%20the%202014%20general%20elections%2C%20not%20only%20removed%20him%20from%20the%20position%20of%20deputy%20CM%20but%20also%20relegated%20him%20to%20insignificance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20months%20after%20his%20removal%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Ckey%E2%80%9D%20BJP%20leader%2C%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20He%20has%20a%20peripheral%20role%20to%20play%20in%20the%20party%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Chouhan%20%E2%80%93%20a%20five-time%20MP%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbhopal%2F5-time-mp-4-term-cm-what-next-for-shivraj-singh-chouhan%2Farticleshow%2F105916787.cms%5C%22%3Elongest-serving%20chief%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20a%20lesser-known%20party%20MLA%20from%20Ujjain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChouhan%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20increase%20the%20stipend%20from%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Ladli%20Behna%E2%80%99%20scheme%2C%20coupled%20with%20his%20intense%20campaigning%2C%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20provided%20traction%20to%20his%20party%20against%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Chouhan%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20Sushil%20Modi%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20noteworthy%20that%20Sushil%20Modi%20enjoys%20the%20unique%20distinction%20of%20never%20losing%20an%20election%2C%20whether%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20in%20the%20assemb