%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20like%20Chouhan%20and%20Sushil%20Modi%2C%20who%20rose%20to%20prominence%20during%20the%20era%20of%20A.B.%20Vajpayee%20and%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20were%20significant%20figures%20in%20the%20BJP%20in%20their%20respective%20states%20before%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20prime%20minister%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20arises%20whether%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20is%20deliberately%20sidelining%20these%20experienced%20leaders%20for%20a%20generational%20change%2C%20to%20introduce%20new%20faces%20and%20promote%20freshness%20within%20the%20party.%20Is%20this%20a%20strategy%20to%20counter%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-nitish-kumar-is-keeping-the-issue-of-bihar-caste-survey-alive%5C%22%3Ecaste-based%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%2065%25%20reservation%20for%20backward%20classes%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%20a%20move%20embraced%20by%20parties%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20as%20a%20counter%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20politics%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Gorakhpur-based%20senior%20RSS-BJP%20leader%20and%20staunch%20loyalist%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20Yogi%20told%20this%20writer%2C%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20%E2%80%9CNarendra%20Modi%20is%20systematically%20sidelining%20all%20the%20senior%20and%20strong%20leaders%20with%20the%20sole%20purpose%20to%20return%20to%20power%20in%202024.%20He%20feels%20threatened%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20superior%20pedigree%20and%20has%20been%20working%20in%20a%20ruthless%20manner%20to%20remove%20the%20%E2%80%98obstacles%E2%80%99%20from%20his%20way%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20polls.%20And%2C%20he%20has%20got%20Amit%20Shah%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98best%20hatchet%20man%E2%80%99%20to%20do%20the%20job%20for%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20has%20captured%20the%20party%20and%20the%20RSS%2C%20too.%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20have%20grown%20in%20power%20but%20the%20BJP%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20democratic%20party%20that%20it%20used%20to%20be%20during%20the%20Vajpayee-Advani%20era%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20observation%20made%20by%20the%20person%20cited%20above%20echoes%20the%20sentiments%20of%20supporters%20of%20Adityanath%2C%20who%20has%20established%20his%20own%20network%20of%20followers%20drawn%20from%20his%20Hindu%20Vahini%2C%20for%20whom%20he%20is%20perceived%20as%20more%20significant%20than%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Adityanath%20loyalists%20at%20Bareilly%20also%20confided%2C%20of%20course%20in%20confidence%2C%20that%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20%E2%80%9Chated%E2%80%9D%20Adityanath.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMaharaj%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Adityanath)%20was%20never%20their%20(Modi%20and%20Shah%E2%80%99s)%20first%20choice.%20They%20wanted%20to%20make%20Manoj%20Sinha%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%202017.%20But%20because%20of%20%5BAdityanath%E2%80%99s%5D%20strong%20network%20of%20loyalists%2C%20they%20failed%20to%20do%20so.%20Modi%20resorted%20to%20several%20devious%20mechanisms%20to%20sideline%20Adityanath%20during%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%202022%20assembly%20elections.%20Very%20reluctantly%2C%20they%20projected%20him%C2%A0as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20during%20the%202022%20polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20Adityanath%20loyalist%20in%20Bareilly%20told%20this%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F25181221%2FFOsK1SjaUAId1Ex.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F25181221%2FFOsK1SjaUAId1Ex.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-con