n%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20respectively%2C%20as%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cmasterstroke%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20politics%20of%20social%20justice%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20However%2C%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20concurrent%20history%20reveals%20that%20there%20is%20no%20%E2%80%9Cnovelty%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohan%20Yadav%20is%20not%20the%20first%20Yadav%20chief%20minister%3B%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%20Babulal%20Gaur%2C%20a%20Yadav%2C%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20over%20a%20year%20from%202004%20to%202005.%20Chouhan%20was%20an%20OBC%20leader%2C%20and%20so%20was%20Uma%20Bharti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20made%20significant%20inroads%20in%20the%20OBC%20vote%20bank%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20However%2C%20this%20success%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20social%20justice%20movement%20in%20MP%2C%20unlike%20in%20Bihar.%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%20had%20endorsed%20Sharad%20Yadav%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CPeople%E2%80%99s%20Candidate%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Bhopal%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20during%20the%201974%20by-election.%20Sharad%20won%20the%20polls%20and%20repeated%20his%20victory%20in%201977.%20However%2C%20he%20abandoned%20the%20social%20justice%20movement%20in%20his%20own%20state%2C%20relocating%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%2C%20leaving%20a%20leadership%20%E2%80%9Cvoid%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20the%20credit%20goes%20to%20the%20RSS-BJP%20for%20exploiting%20this%20void%20and%20creating%20its%20own%20brand%20of%20leaders%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20marking%20the%20real%20strength%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702467944000%2C%22visu