-ravi-bishnois-omission-in-2nd-t20i%2Farticleshow%2F105963548.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20earning%20the%20player%20of%20the%20series%20accolade%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20T20I%20series%20against%20Australia%20at%20home%2C%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%20did%20not%20secure%20a%20spot%20in%20Team%20India's%20playing%20XI%20for%20the%20second%20T20I%20against%20South%20Africa%20on%20Tuesday.%20His%20impressive%20performance%2C%20yielding%209%20wickets%20against%20Australia%2C%20also%20resulted%20in%20him%20surpassing%20Afghanistan's%20star%20spinner%20Rashid%20Khan%2C%20propelling%20Bishnoi%20to%20the%20coveted%20position%20of%20the%20world's%20No.%201%20T20I%20bowler.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-south-africa%2Fyes-he-is-the-no-1-bowler-in-the-world-but-sunil-gavaskar-on-ravi-bishnois-omission-in-2nd-t20i%2Farticleshow%2F105963548.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Article%20370%20Judgment%20-%20Boost%20For%20India%20On%20Global%20Stage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20process%20that%20started%20in%20August%202019%20finally%20culminated%20this%20week%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20placed%20its%20seal%20of%20approval%20on%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20decision%20to%20revoke%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20On%205%20August%202019%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20announced%20in%20parliament%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20had%20exempted%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20from%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20(except%20Article%201%20and%20Article%20370%20itself)%20and%20permitted%20the%20state%20to%20draft%20its%20own%20Constitution.%20The%20state%20was%20bifurcated%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%20-%20Ladakh%20without%20a%20legislature%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20with%20a%20legislature.%20It%20was%20a%20transformative%20move%20and%20predictably%20generated%20strong%20passions%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20leading%20to%20challenges%20in%20court.%20Since%20August%2C%20the%20constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20taken%20up%20nearly%2023%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20government's%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20that%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bculmination%20of%20the%20process%20of%20integration%26quot%3B%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20with%20the%20Union%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20this%20week%20declared%20that%20there%20was%20no%20malafide%20intention%20in%20declaring%20this%20article%20inoperative.%20The%20Constitution%20bench%20upheld%20the%20power%20of%20the%20President%20of%20India%20to%20unilaterally%20dilute%20special%20status%20accorded%20to%20the%20former%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20per%20Article%20370.%20The%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20land%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20%26quot%3Bsurrendered%26quot%3B%20its%20sovereignty%20%26quot%3Bfull%20and%20final%26quot%3B%20when%20a%20proclamation%20was%20issued%20for%20the%20state%20on%2025%20November%201949%2C%20and%20that%20Article%20370%20was%20a%20temporary%20provision%20-%20an%20interim%20arrangement%20due%20to%20war%20conditions%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPartisan%20politics%20on%20this%20matter%20will%20continue%20despite%20the%20verdict%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20drawn%20a%20line%20under%20the%20issue.%20In%20more%20than%20ways%20than%20one%2C%20it%20strengthens%20the%20position%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20as%20a%20leader%20who%20is%20serious%20about%20finding%20decisive%20solutions%20to%20India's%20domestic%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20quo%20on%20Kashmir%20had%20become%20unsustainable%20long%20back.%20It%20was%20only%20the%20political%20and%20policy%20inertia%20that%20was%20keeping%20Indian%20policymakers%20from%20challenging%20that.%20The%20so-called%20problem%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20always%20been%20a%20bilateral%20matter%20between%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20rest%20of%20India%20has%20been%20living%20with%20one%20set%20of%20policies%20vis-a-vis%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20the%20last%20seven%20decades%20and%20the%20results%20have%20been%20underwhelming.%20Just%20as%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20India%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20too%20has%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Modi%20government%20had%20underlined%20that%20it%20is%20not%20only%20serious%20about%20consolidating%20India's%20frayed%20peripheries%20but%20is%20also%20cognizant%20of%20the%20aspirations%20of%20a%20state%2C%20which%2C%20despite%20its%20resources%2C%20has%20become%20a%20cesspool%20of%20violence%20and%20degenerative%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20government's%20reform%20agenda%20is%20critically%20important%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20for%20India's%20own%20future.%20And%20its%20full%20operationalisation%20will%20take%20time%20but%20the%20results%20are%20already%20visible%20in%20declining%20violence%2C%20rapid%20pace%20of%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20and%20growing%20tourist%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20critics%20in%20India%20continue%20to%20crib%20about%20government%20measures%2C%20their%20seriousness%20of%20intent%20is%20well-appreciated%20by%20India's%20adversaries.%20After%20all%2C%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20China%20upped%20the%20ante%20in%20Ladakh%20was%20in%20recognition%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20these%20measures%20can%20fundamentally%20alter%20India's%20strategic%20periphery%20to%20China's%20long-term%20detriment.%20India%20is%20finally%20making%20its%20intent%20clear%20and%20that%20is%20bound%20to%20unnerve%20those%20who%20were%20comfortable%20with%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meltdown%20in%20Pakistan%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20makes%20it%20clear%20how%20irrelevant%20Pakistan%20has%20become%20to%20the%20discourse%20on%20Kashmir.%20For%20all%20its%20tantrums%2C%20it%20had%20long%20lost%20its%20locus%20standi%20on%20the%20matter.%20Now%20all%20the%20posturing%20of%20Pakistani%20politicians%20is%20for%20the%20domestic%20audience.%20Though%20it%20made%20a%20big%20deal%20of%20cutting%20off%20trade%20ties%20with%20India%20and%20recalling%20its%20high%20commissioner%20after%20India's%20decision%20to%20revoke%20Article%20370%2C%20the%20world%20moved%20on%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20impact%20of%20these%20decisions%20except%20to%20make%20Islamabad%20even%20more%20redundant%20in%20the%20Indian%20foreign%20policy%20matrix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Supreme%20Court's%20verdict%2C%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20of%20a%20new%20start%2C%20if%20Pakistan%20recognizes%20the%20new%20realities%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20but%20that%20too%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20till%20the%20election.%20Whatever%20happens%20now%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20terms%20of%20engagement%20will%20be%20set%20by%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20which%20was%20already%20engaging%20with%20India%20as%20a%20rising%20economic%20and%20geopolitical%20player%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20will%20further%20reinforce%20the%20sense%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20wider%20mood%20in%20the%20country%20and%20that%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20key%20lens%20through%20which%20to%20view%20either%20India%20or%20the%20government.%20By%20burying%20Article%20370%2C%20the%20government%20has%20buried%20one%20of%20most%20serious%20challenges%20that%20Indian%20foreign%20policy%20faced%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20for%20the%20more%20than%20seven%20decades.%20The%20Supreme%20Court's%20validation%20of%20the%20move%20couldn't%20have%20come%20at%20a%20better%20time%20for%20Modi.%3