rh%20and%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%20for%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20particular%20have%20been%20consistent%20on%20one%20significant%20count%2C%20one%20that%20has%20been%20hallmark%20of%20the%20current%20regime%20-%20secrecy%20and%20surprise%20in%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20pattern%20in%20these%20picks%20is%20that%20all%20three%20have%20ordinary%20roots%2C%20strong%20organisational%20connect%20and%20a%20relatively%20low%20profile.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20they%20are%20an%20inspirational%20narrative%20for%20ordinary%20party%20workers%20-%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekaryakartas%3C%2Fem%3E%20-%20work%20harder%20and%20the%20sky%20is%20the%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20own%20journey%20has%20been%20no%20less%20an%20inspiration%20to%20the%20cadre.%20By%20introducing%20fresh%20faces%2C%20Modi%20is%20preparing%20the%20party's%20Gen%20Next%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20for%20nothing%20that%20elections%20in%20these%20states%20were%20fought%20in%20the%20name%20of%20collective%20state%20leadership%20with%20PM%20Modi%20as%20the%20face%20under%20the%20slogan%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BModi%20ki%20guarantee%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20voted%20the%20BJP%20didn't%20have%20any%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20to%20influence%20their%20decision.%20It%20was%20for%20PM%20Modi%20to%20appoint%20someone%2C%20on%20their%20behalf%2C%20to%20steer%20the%20state%2C%20to%20deliver%2C%20to%20prove%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20work%20in%20a%20way%20that%20the%20BJP%20can%20maximise%20its%20potential%20in%20next%20year's%20parliamentary%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20general%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2062%20out%20of%2065%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20these%20states.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20it%20would%20like%20a%20perfect%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20caste%20profiles%20of%20the%20designated%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20and%20Speakers%20signals%20a%20larger%20message%20to%20targeted%20social%20constituents%20beyond%20the%20boundaries%20of%20the%20three%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarkable%20victories%20for%20the%20BJP%20have%20already%20robbed%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20opposition%20I.N.D.I.A%20grouping%20of%20its%20biggest%20poll%20plank%2C%20the%20caste%20census.%20Now%20the%20choice%20of%20new%20chief%20ministers%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20more%20dents%20in%20the%20perceived%20social%20support%20base%20of%20rival%20political%20groupings.%20As%20it%20is%2C%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20grouping%20is%20under%20massive%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20analysing%20these%20decisions%20and%20how%20they%20impact%20the%20BJP's%20prospects%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20observing%20how%20the%20current%20dispensation%20in%20the%20BJP%20works%20towards%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Modi's%20mission%20is%20to%20create%20a%20new%20state%20leadership%20structure%2C%20to%20infuse%20fresh%20energy%20and%20carry%20the%20party%20for%20at%20least%20the%20next%20decade.%20He%20has%20done%20so%20with%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20in%20Assam%2C%20Pramod%20Sawant%20in%20Goa%20and%20now%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20right%20from%20the%20time%20some%20union%20ministers%20and%20MPs%20were%20asked%20to%20fight%20assembly%20elections%2C%20with%20or%20without%20their%20consent%2C%20the%20message%20was%20clear.%20The%20party%20is%20supreme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister%20in%202014%2C%20he%20enforced%20a%20decisive%20shift%20in%20the%20way%20a%20ruling%20party%20works.%20In%20regimes%20prior%2C%20once%20a%20party%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20entire%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20government%20and%20there%20was%20little%20attention%20on%20organisation%20and%20organisational%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Amit%20Shah%20taking%20over%20as%20BJP%20president%20in%202014%20(till%20the%202019%20polls)%2C%20much%20changed.%20The%20organisation%20gained%20a%20new%20aura%20and%20a%20new%20command%20and%20control.%20It%20continues%20to%20work%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20it%20is%20becoming%20apparent%20to%20the%20party%20rank%20and%20file%20that%20lobbying%20and%20pressuring%20the%20Modi-Shah%20dispensation%20is%20sure%20to%20be%20counterproductive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20anyone%20rooted%20to%20ground%20and%20diligent%20can%20be%20picked%20up%20for%20top%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20a%20leader%20has%20to%20be%20in%20perfect%20sync%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3ESarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESangathan%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20(government%20and%20organisation)%20to%20make%20a%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Chief%20Minister%20Picks%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohan%20Yadav's%20rise%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20stunning%20even%20for%20newly-elected%20BJP%20MLAs%2C%20their%20supporters%20and%20ordinary%20party%20workers.%20He%20was%20chosen%20over%20four-time%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20union%20ministers%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20and%20Prahlad%20Patel%2C%20national%20general%20secretary%20Kailash%20Vijayvargia%20and%20a%20few%20more%20heavyweights.%20He%20was%2C%20like%20his%20compatriots%2C%20completely%20unaware%20of%20what%20was%20in%20store%20for%20him.%20In%20the%20group%20photo%20of%20newly%20elected%20legislators%20with%20central%20leaders%2C%20Yadav%20was%20seated%20in%20a%20corner%20of%20the%20third%20row.%20So%20overwhelmed%20he%20was%20that%20he%20could%20barely%20find%20words%20when%20he%20came%20to%20the%20podium%2C%20or%20before%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Yadav%20in%20charge%20of%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20states%20of%20the%20country%20is%20a%20neon%20sign%20to%20the%20Yadav%20community%2C%20particularly%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar.%20In%20UP%2C%20the%20Yadav%20community%20is%20strongly%20aligned%20to%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20The%20Samajwadi%20party's%20politics%20is%20primarily%20based%20on%20its%20Muslim-Yadav%20support%20base.%20The%20same%20for%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20RJD%20in%20Bihar.%20It's%20also%20true%20that%20sections%20of%20Yadavs%20vote%20for%20Modi%20in%20parliamentary%20elections%20but%20that%20is%20the%20only%20caste%20among%20Hindus%20that%20have%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20BJP%20in%20UP%20and%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohan%20Yadav's%20elevation%20can%20potentially%20initiate%20a%20churning%20in%20this%20community's%20thought%20process%2C%20impel%20them%20to%20look%20away%20from%20the%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20and%20Lalu%20dynasty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20naming%20of%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20a%20Rajput%2C%20as%20Speaker%20and%20two%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20-%20Jagdish%20Devda%2C%20a%20Dalit%20and%20Rajendra%20Shukla%2C%20a%20Brahmin%20-%20reflects%20intricate%20caste%20and%20community%20balancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChhattisgarh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20making%20tribal%20leader%20Vishnu%20Dev%20Sai%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Modi%20has%20reaffirmed%20the%20trust%20tribal%20community%20placed%20in%20him%20in%20these%20elections.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2017%20of%2029%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20seats%2C%20and%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20party%20won%2027%20of%2047%20Schedule%20Tribe%20seats.%20In%20Rajasthan%20too%2C%20the%20community%20leaned%20more%20towards%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20been%20actively%20working%20on%20his%20tribal%20outreach%20since%20he%20came%20to%20power%2C%20and%20more%20vigorously%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20The%20selection%20of%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20a%20self-made%20tribal%20leader%20who%20came%20up%20the%20ladder%20through%20grit%2C%20passion%20and%20hard%20work%20as%20the%20presidential%20candidate%20of%20the%20ruling%20NDA%2C%20and%20her%20subsequent%20election%20with%20a%20record%20margin%20was%20a%20big%20message%20to%20the%20tribal%20community%20in%20particular%20and%20the%20society%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20height%20of%20the%20campaign%2C%20Modi%20flew%20to%20iconic%20tribal%20leader%20Birsa%20Munda's%20birthplace%20Khunti%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20launched%20a%20mega%20tribal%20outreach%20program%20-%20the%20Rs%2024%2C000%20crore%20mission%20aimed%20at%20benefiting%202.8%20million%20people%20from%20particularly%20vulnerable%20tribal%20groups%20(PVTGs)%20across%20220%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20tribal%20communities%20form%208.6%25%20of%20the%20country's%20population%20and%2047%20of%20543%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20are%20reserved%20for%20them.%20Tribal%20dominated%20Jharkhand%20will%20vote%20immediately%20after%20the%20national%20election%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20social%20balancing%2C%20Arun%20Sao%20from%20the%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20community%20and%20Vijay%20Sharma%20from%20the%20upper%20caste%20are%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20and%20Raman%20Singh%2C%20who%20had%20been%20Chief%20Minister%20for%2010%20years%2C%20will%20be%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20choosing%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20first%20time%20MLA%20with%20a%20strong%20organisational%20connect%2C%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20signalled%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20top%20slot%2C%20there%20is%20no%20bar.%20Sharma%20is%20a%20Brahmin%3B%20his%20ascension%20sends%20a%20strong%20signal%20to%20the%20upper%20castes%20not%20just%20in%20Rajasthan%20but%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20as%20well.%20The%20Brahmins%20and%20other%20upper%20castes%20have%20long%20shifted%20their%20loyalty%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20earlier%20given%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20in%20upper%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20for%20balance%2C%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%20a%20Rajput%20and%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%2C%20a%20Dalit%2C%20have%20been%20named%20deputies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi's%20idea%20is%20to%20consolidate%20the%20party's%20existing%20social%20support%20base%20and%20breach%20new%20boundaries.%20His%20picks%20need%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702467360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fcsdv1rag_rajasthan-new-cm-bhajan-lal-sharma-_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmany-signs-and-messages-behind-bjps-triple-surprise-4659989%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20introducing%20fresh%20faces%2C%20Modi%20is%20preparing%20the%20party's%20Gen%20Next%20leadership.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmany-signs-and-messages-behind-bjps-triple-surprise-4659989%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmany-signs-and-messages-behind-bjps-triple-surprise-4659989%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmany-signs-and-messages-behind-bjps-triple-surprise-4659989%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAre%20All%20Lives%20Not%20Equal%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Khawaja%20On%20ICC%20Threat%20Over%20'Gaza%20Message'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralia%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Usman%20Khawaja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1414-usman-khawaja-playerprofile%5C%22%3EUsman%20Khawaja%3C%