s%20in%20the%20Twin%20Cities%20and%20beyond%2C''%20US%20Representative%20Betty%20McCollum%20(D-Minnesota)%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20condoling%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20devastating%20news.%20My%20heart%20goes%20out%20to%20Tou%20Ger%20Xiong's%20family%20%26amp%3B%20our%20entire%20Hmong%20community.%20As%20a%20comedian%20and%20activist%2C%20his%20work%20touched%20many%20lives%20in%20the%20Twin%20Cities%20and%20beyond.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FA4ZBMi3sSV%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FA4ZBMi3sSV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rep.%20Betty%20McCollum%20(%40BettyMcCollum04)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBettyMcCollum04%2Fstatus%2F1734700934914023466%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Xiong%20was%20a%20Laotian-American%20comedian%2C%20educator%2C%20and%20comedian%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20St.%20Paul%2C%20Minnesota.%20He%20was%20known%20for%20his%20advocacy%20for%20the%20Hmong%20people%2C%20an%20indigenous%20group%20that%20lives%20primarily%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKidnappings%20in%20Colombia%20are%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20according%20to%20authorities.%C2%A0Three%20American%20tourists%2C%20including%20Mr%20Xiong%2C%20have%20been%20murdered%20in%20the%20last%20month%2C%20El%20Colombiano%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702463640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fbaeqrho8_-tou-ger-xiong_625x300_13_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-comedian-kidnapped-and-killed-in-colombia-after-going-on-a-date-with-a-woman-4666140%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22His%20body%20was%20found%20in%20the%20waters%20of%20the%20La%20Corcovado%20ravine%20with%20multiple%20stab%20wounds%20and%20blunt-force%20trauma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engage