%20little%20slingshot%20will%20break-up%20thousands%20of%20families%2C%20keep%20children%20away%20from%20parents%20and%20disrupt%20many%20romances%20which%20could%20result%20in%20life-long%20partnerships%20and%20happiness.%20I%20should%20declare%20an%20interest%20%E2%80%93%20my%20wife%20is%20not%20British%20by%20birth%20or%20passport.%20The%20same%20could%20be%20said%2C%20of%20course%2C%20for%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20happened%3F%20Well%2C%20last%20week%2C%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20package%20of%20measures%20designed%20to%20limit%20immigration%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20that%20the%20minimum%20income%20required%20to%20bring%20a%20foreign%20spouse%20into%20the%20country%20on%20a%20family%20visa%20will%20rise%20sharply%20to%20%C2%A338%2C700%20(about%20Rs%2040%20lakh)%20a%20year.%20That%20figure%20is%20well%20above%20the%20average%20income.%20Outside%20London%2C%20not%20even%20one-in-four%20full-time%20workers%20earn%20that%20much.%20So%20in%20a%20nutshell%2C%20most%20Brits%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20eligible%20to%20sponsor%20their%20foreign%20wife%20or%20husband%20to%20live%2C%20or%20stay%2C%20in%20Britain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20will%20be%20introduced%2C%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20rethink%2C%20in%20a%20few%20months%E2%80%99%20time.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20threshold%20for%20eligibility%20to%20get%20a%20visa%20for%20a%20spouse%20is%20earnings%20of%20%C2%A318%2C600%20(about%20Rs%2020%20lakh)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20nine-in-ten%20of%20those%20in%20full-time%20work%20meet.%20Those%20foreign%20spouses%20who%20already%20have%20indefinite%20leave%20to%20remain%2C%20or%20have%20become%20British%20nationals%2C%20will%20not%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20new%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20change%20will%20not%20have%20much%20effect%20on%20the%20number%20of%20migrants%20%E2%80%93%20it%20may%20cut%20the%20number%20of%20family%20visas%20issued%20a%20year%20by%20about%2010%2C000.%20But