%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Ff1cce7e5-ad7b-4cb0-b738-4e88a361b637%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702536247409000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw36Bu42irecVElcXdZGkC5L%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0ensured%20a%20similar%20victory%20in%20impending%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20master%20wordsmith%2C%20Modi%20aim%20was%20to%20throw%20the%20opposition%20into%20disarray.%20And%20his%20talking%20up%20the%20%E2%80%98hat-trick%E2%80%99%20worked.%20Played%20up%20by%20TV%20channels%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20instantly%20announced%20she%20would%20not%20attend%20joint%20opposition%20meetings%20%E2%80%98anymore%E2%80%99.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20even%20declared%20a%20boycott%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fba36abeb-4bc4-464a-a972-05a4ba407c7a%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fba36abeb-4bc4-464a-a972-05a4ba407c7a%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702536247409000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw05eo_qZzHfIm08WtXe_-zz%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0future%20opposition%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20had%20to%20put%20off%20its%20meeting%20scheduled%20for%20December%206.%20%E2%80%9CKnives%20are%20out%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20TV%20channels%20gleefully%20declared.%20The%20Congress%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20confusion%20by%20fixing%20the%20December%206%20meeting%20without%20consulting%20even%20senior%20allies%20like%20M.K.%20Stalin%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20does%20the%20triumph%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhatisgarh%20really%20ensure%20a%20BJP%20victory%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20Modi%20claims%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20closer%20look%20at%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20shows%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20already%20reached%20saturation%20point%20in%20all%20Hindi%20states.%20There%20is%20no%20room%20for%20further%20improvement%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%2025%20out%20of%2025%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%2028%20out%20of%2029%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20nine%20of%2011%20in%20Chhatisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20party%20bagged%20all%20seven%20seats%2C%20all%2010%20in%20Haryana%2C%20and%20all%2026%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%202019%20Balakot%20bravado%20had%20its%20impact%20on%20outlying%20states%20in%20the%20south%20and%20even%20in%20opposition%20strongholds%20like%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Bihar.%20The%20BJP%20cannot%20achieve%20these%20figures%20without%20precipitating%20a%20similar%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPsephologist%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20has%20also%20turned%20to%20vote%20shares%20to%20argue%20why%20Modi%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fce9a9974-e894-4220-bf77-801a2d362371%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fce9a9974-e894-4220-bf77-801a2d362371%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702536247409000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0e5tfZuzghCFsRipbpUe6G%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%98hat%20trick%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20theory%20was%20flawed.%20The%20difference%20between%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20was%20less%20than%202%25%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%204%25%20in%20Chhatisgarh.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20retained%20power%2C%20the%20difference%20was%20a%20respectable%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20explains%20this%20gulf%20between%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20votes%3F%20While%20there%20can%20be%20many%20factors%2C%20there%20are%20three%20which%20need%20highlighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20setting%20in%20motion%20ED%2FCBI%2FIT%20raids%20not%20just%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20an%20election%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20been%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20practice%20%E2%80%93%20but%20even%20after%20the%20election%20process%20has%20begun.%20This%20marks%20the%20start%20of%20a%20dangerous%20new%20strategy.%20It%20amounts%20to%20intentionally%20disrupting%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20legitimate%20election%20work%20by%20way%20of%20choking%20the%20flow%20of%20funds%20and%20arbitrarily%20seizing%20campaign%20materials.%20All%20the%20while%20allowing%20the%20ruling%20party%20a%20free%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20ban%20by%20the%20EC%20on%20the%20introduction%20of%20new%20government%20largesse%20after%20elections%20have%20been%20announced.%20There%20is%20little%20chance%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20accepting%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20a%20similar%20ban%20on%20ED%2FCBI%2FIncome%20tax%20assaults%20during%20the%20elections.%20Look%20at%20the%20way%20the%20ED%2FCBI%20hounded%20the%20opposition%20during%20the%20elections%20while%20treating%20BJP%20leaders%20with%20kid%20gloves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20disrupt%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20election%20work%2C%20the%20ED%2C%20CBI%2C%20and%20income%20tax%20intensified%20raids%20on%20its%20leaders%2C%20including%20candidates.%20They%20were%20harassed%20and%20put%20under%20strain%20while%20not%20a%20single%20BJP%20leader%20was%20subjected%20to%20similar%20treatment.%20The%20ED%2FCBI%2FIT%20cannot%20demoralise%20Congress%20workers%2C%20says%20Kharge.%20But%20they%20did%20frustrate%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20and%20it%20did%20disrupt%20their%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20these%20assembly%20elections%20heralded%20another%2C%20far%20more%20alarming%20trend.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20party%20has%20field-tested%20a%20cloak-and-dagger%20%E2%80%98influence%E2%80%99%20operation%20aimed%20at%20sabotaging%20the%20political%20fortunes%20of%20its%20rivals.%C2%A0The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F41fda598-c7f9-4427-a398-492fcc2aa844%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%3ELokniti%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20referred%20to%20a%20sudden%20swing%20in%20voters%E2%80%99%20mood%20some%20time%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20November.%20Development%20issues%2C%20which%20were%20the%20dominant%20theme%20earlier%2C%20took%20a%20back%20seat%20after%20November%203%20(four%20days%20before%20the%20polling%20on%20November%207)%20when%20the%20ED%20came%20out%20with%20its%20allegation%20of%20a%20Rs%20508%20crore%20%E2%80%98Mahadev%20scam%E2%80%99%20against%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20should%20draw%20the%20right%20lessons%20from%20this%20episode.%20This%20must%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20rehearsal%20for%20more%20daring%20influence%20operations%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20the%20present%20regime%E2%80%99s%20proclivity%20to%20undertake%20audacious%20operations%20even%20in%20foreign%20lands.%C2%A0This%20has%20led%20to%C2%A0much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fdde7635b-dfbd-41ea-97ec-fd10bf477294%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%3Ediplomatic%20tension%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20friendly%20countries.%20This%20adds%20to%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20fears%20of%20a%20last-minute%20Modi%20gambit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20the%20Electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20virtually%20legalises%20unaccounted%20money%20and%20puts%20it%20into%20the%20kitty%20of%20the%20preferred%20political%20party.%20The%20sale%20of%20the%20latest%20tranche%20of%20bonds%20happened%20in%20November%2C%20just%20in%20ti