0and%20social%20media%20posts%20claiming%20to%20reveal%20the%20personal%20relationships%20and%20funding%20sources%20behind%20U.S.-based%20critics%20of%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Disinfo%20Lab%20%E2%80%9Ccombined%20fact-based%20research%20with%20unsubstantiated%20claims%20to%20paint%20U.S.%20government%20figures%2C%20researchers%2C%20humanitarian%20groups%20and%20Indian%20American%20rights%20activists%20as%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%2C%20purportedly%20led%20by%20global%20Islamic%20groups%20and%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%2C%20to%20undermine%20India.%E2%80%9D%20The%20news%20report%20records%20how%20these%20allegations%20went%20viral%20on%20Indian%20social%20media%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20they%20were%20amplified%20by%20pro-Modi%20influencers%2C%20who%20at%20times%20used%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20findings%20to%20validate%20their%20own%20positions.%20Its%20reports%20have%20been%20cited%20by%20Indian%20officials%20on%20television%20and%20presented%20on%20Capitol%20Hill.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Disinfo%20Lab%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20disclose%20its%20affiliation%2C%20describing%20itself%20on%20its%20website%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98separate%20legal%20entity%E2%80%99%20that%20seeks%20to%20offer%20%E2%80%98completely%20unbiased%20research.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20the%20newspaper%20records%20how%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20media%20researchers%20have%20uncovered%20large%20Indian%20online%20networks%20that%20promote%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20policy%20positions%20to%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20audiences.%E2%80%9D%20Coordinated%20social%20media%20accounts%20have%20been%20found%20to%20play%20a%20role%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20in%20spreading%20identical%20posts%20in%20support%20of%20Russia%2C%20an%20important%20supplier%20of%20weapons%20and%20energy%20to%20India%2C%20and%20of%20Israel%2C%20an%20increasingly%20close%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatpathy%20is%20said%20to%20have%20met%20%E2%80%9CWestern%20journalists%20and%20commentators%20under%20fake%20identities%20%E2%80%94%20including%20his%20preferred%20alias%2C%20Shakti%2C%20meaning%20%E2%80%9Cpower%E2%80%9D%20in%20Hindi%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sought%20favorable%20coverage%20of%20India%20or%20critical%20coverage%20of%20its%20adversaries%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20China%2C%20according%20to%20five%20additional%20people%20who%20have%20had%20contact%20with%20Satpathy.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Disinfo%20Lab%20though%2C%20denies%20any%20connection%20with%20government%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20in%20no%20form%20associated%20with%20any%20govt%20agency%2C%20nor%20with%20any%20of%20its%20personnel.%20Nor%20are%20we%20associated%20with%20any%20other%20organization%20%E2%80%94%20Indian%20or%20International%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20told%20the%20Post.%20It%20said%20it%20was%20created%20by%20individuals%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20had%20met%20in%20an%20anti-corruption%20political%20movement%E2%80%9D%20and%20were%20concerned%20about%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20massive%20disinformation%20targeted%20at%20India%20to%20sow%20divisions%20in%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDisinfoLab%2Fstatus%2F1734075357144498602%5C%22%3EOn%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Disinfo%20Lab%20called%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbarely%20disguised%20revenge%20piece%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20right%20wing%20is%20a%20new%20player%20that%20has%20arrived%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20and%20wants%20to%20shape%20global%20discussion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joyojeet%20Pal%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20information%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%20who%20studies%20disinformation%20in%20India%20is%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20much%20of%20it%20is%20done%20in%20the%20same%20way%20it%E2%80%99s%20done%20within%20India%20%E2%80%94%20through%20crude%2C%20blunt%20force.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20getting%20smarter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Disinfo%20Lab%20has%20emerged%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20more%20sophisticated%20players%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20avers%20as%20in%20it%20%E2%80%9C28%20reports%20it%20has%20published%20so%20far%2C%20the%20organization%20has%20often%20painted%20a%20picture%20of%20an%20India%20under%20attack%20by%20a%20sprawling%20%E2%80%9Cnexus%E2%80%9D%20of%20conspirators%20funded%20by%20Pakistani%20intelligence%2C%20the%20Muslim%20Brotherhood%20and%20Soros.%E2%80%9D%20The%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20of%20the%20influential%20retweeters%2C%20end%20up%20giving%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Disinfo%20Lab%20a%20stamp%20of%20authority%20and%2C%20some%20of%20its%20targets%20say%2C%20boost%20its%20ability%20to%20intimidate%20individuals%20overseas%E2%80%9D%2C%20when%20in%20effect%20it%20is%20allegedly%20connected%20with%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20operation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumit%20Ganguly%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20Indian%20diplomacy%20and%20national%20security%20at%20Indiana%20University%20at%20Bloomington%20in%20the%20US%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20undermining%20foreign%20governments%20and%20their%20officials%20is%20%E2%80%9Croutine%E2%80%9D%20work%20for%20all%20intelligence%20agencies.%20But%2C%20he%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying%2C%20if%20Indian%20intelligence%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbesmirching%20American%20critics%20and%20civil%20society%20organizations%2C%20it%20would%20be%20crossing%20a%20line%20reminiscent%20of%20KGB%20tactics%20during%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20part%20and%20parcel%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20toward%20dissent%2C%20whether%20at%20home%20or%20abroad.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatpathy%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20comments.%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20adviser%2C%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20too%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702445818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.th