l%20hardships%20in%20the%20family.%20So%20he%20chose%20to%20stick%20to%20his%20roots%20and%20continue%20the%20family%20business%2C%20unlike%20many%20of%20his%20peers%20who%20migrated%20to%20the%20nearby%20Bengaluru%20city%20for%20odd%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20present-day%20%3Cem%3Eidli%3C%2Fem%3E%20makers%2C%20steamers%20and%20containers%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20says%20that%20his%20family%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309836%2Ffood-history-of-idli-sambar-roots-in-indonesia-south-indian-breakfast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esteam%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20small%20bamboo%20baskets%2C%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Kannada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVatsala%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBamboo%20is%20available%20in%20abundance%20in%20our%20village.%20The%20villagers%20make%20and%20sell%20many%20items%20made%20using%20bamboo.%20That%E2%80%99s%20probably%20why%20my%20ancestors%20chose%20to%20utilise%20bamboo%20containers%20to%20make%20idlis%20back%20then.%20Moreover%20using%20bamboo%20makes%20the%20process%20very%20natural.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20unique%20preparation%20method%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20pour%20the%20batter%20into%20the%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20They%20are%20small%20bowl-shaped%20moulds%20made%20using%20bamboo.%20The%20container%20gives%20the%20batter%20a%20perfect%20idli%20shape.%20We%20then%20place%20these%20small%20bamboo%20bowls%20into%20a%20large%20aluminium%20utensil%20using%20bamboo%20sticks%20for%20support.%20Then%20we%20let%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20slowly%20steam%20over%20firewood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fculinaryjourneybynaveen%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0Jhj3eTm6mx67S7cyYDkhocjFkLTESKhrX8GoMGENaQ