nd%20I%20cannot%2C%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20think%20of%20opening%20any%20other%20branches.%20In%20fact%2C%20now%20I%20am%20scared%20of%20the%20social%20media%20reach%20because%20my%20only%20hope%20to%20keep%20this%20place%20up%20is%20if%20I%20get%20reliable%20employees%20or%20volunteers%20to%20share%20the%20load.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Vatsala%20feels%20fulfilled%20looking%20back%20at%20a%20life%20of%20service%2C%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20dedication%20to%20his%20family%20and%20business.%20He%20finds%20joy%20in%20having%20transformed%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20business%20into%20a%20lasting%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20help%20Bhakta%20Vatsala%20keep%20%E2%80%98Babu%20Hotel%E2%80%99%20running%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20him%20here%3A%20%2B91%2098863%2075522.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700833878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Located%20in%20Halaguru%20village%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20Babu%20Hotel%20has%20served%20chiblu%20idlis%20made%20in%20bamboo%20baskets%20for%20over%20seven%20decades.%20Its%20owner%20Bhakta%20Vatsala%20shares%20what%20makes%20these%20idlis%20unique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334919%2Fchiblu-idlis-in-bamboo-bengaluru-babu-hotel-halaguru-village-in-karnataka%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Biggest%20Rapper%20Moko%20Koza%20Chose%20Hip%20Hop%20Over%20MBBS%20To%20Speak%20for%20His%20People%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMv%C3%BCko%20Koza%2C%20a%20Kohima-based%20multilingual%20recording%20artist%20and%20songwriter%2C%20who%20popularly%20goes%20by%20Moko%20Koza%2C%20has%20never