a.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334806%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaloni%20is%20posted%20as%20the%20district%20collector%20of%20Mandla%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20aspirants%2C%20Saloni%20says%2C%20she%20was%20not%20obsessed%20with%20the%20preparation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20dedicated%20and%20sincere%20to%20my%20preparation%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20was%20relaxed%20and%20not%20stressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20helped%20her%20crack%20the%20examination%20in%20the%20very%20first%20attempt%2C%20Saloni%20says%2C%20was%20her%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%2C%20I%20would%20dedicate%20around%20six%20to%20eight%20hours%20to%20preparation.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20single%20day%20when%20I%20took%20an%20off.%20Usually%2C%20some%20people%20study%20for%2012%20hours%20one%20day%20and%20then%20waste%20time%20sleeping%20for%20the%20entire%20next%20day.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESeek%20guidance%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20if%20you%20want%20to%20take%20support%20from%20coaching.%20Personally%2C%20I%20preferred%20joining%20a%20coaching%20institute%20where%20they%20had%20very%20less%20aspirants%2C%20instead%20of%20going%20to%20a%20class%20of%20400%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saloni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20only%20had%20five%20months%20to%20appear%20for%20prelims.%20I%20would%20seclude%20myself%20in%20a%20library%2C%20away%20from%20the%20chaos%20of%20aspirants%20who%20keep%20advising%20others%20to%20follow%20this%20or%20that%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%201